0:00:00.000,0:00:07.040
A woman and her two young children were seen outside The SCOAN,

0:00:07.040,0:00:12.620
distressed and in a very emotional state late at night.

0:00:12.620,0:00:19.020
The attention of the Emmanuel TV team was called to their case and they came to find out what had happened

0:00:19.020,0:00:20.600
to this family.

0:00:20.600,0:00:22.000
Let us listen to them.

0:00:22.000,0:00:24.240
My name is Christie Pua.

0:00:24.240,0:00:27.020
I came from Indonesia.

0:00:27.020,0:00:29.700
And who are the two people standing beside you?

0:00:29.700,0:00:34.300
They are my children; Fredrick and Blessing.

0:00:34.300,0:00:40.120
Can you explain the reason why you have come to The SCOAN this evening?

0:00:40.120,0:00:43.240
I am looking for favour from the man of God.

0:00:43.240,0:00:45.160
We have been living here.

0:00:45.160,0:00:50.420
We have run from the village because they accused my husband for being a murderer -

0:00:50.420,0:00:53.020
that he killed his own father.

0:00:53.020,0:01:00.800
After a few months, his niece died and they accused my husband for being the murderer who killed his niece.

0:01:00.800,0:01:06.160
That is why we ran away from the village to Lagos without anything.

0:01:06.160,0:01:11.080
We managed to sell the remaining things in the house only for the transport money.

0:01:11.080,0:01:18.100
Now, we have become like beggars in Lagos – we don't have any place to stay.

0:01:18.100,0:01:22.960
That is why we ran here – we want to look for the favour of the man of God.

0:01:22.960,0:01:25.000
Who is the father of the children?

0:01:25.000,0:01:29.000
His name is John Ken Egesi from Imo State.

0:01:29.000,0:01:32.620
I have been married to him for the past 16 years.

0:01:32.620,0:01:35.380
How did you meet with him?

0:01:35.380,0:01:40.440
We met in Indonesia when he was doing his business.

0:01:40.440,0:01:46.660
He was selling garments and exporting clothes.

0:01:46.660,0:01:56.860
Some years after we married, he said I should come and be introduced to his family in Nigeria.

0:01:56.860,0:02:06.800
I have been here for the past five years, living in Imo State with him, suffering.

0:02:06.800,0:02:14.040
The worst part now is that they accused my husband of murdering his own father and niece.

0:02:14.040,0:02:15.400
That is why we are here now.

0:02:15.400,0:02:17.460
We have no other place.

0:02:17.460,0:02:20.140
My husband is just hustling.

0:02:20.140,0:02:26.240
Sometimes he goes to Alaba and at the end of the day, he brings only 100 or 200 naira.

0:02:26.240,0:02:30.100
How can we eat with 200 naira with these kids?

0:02:30.100,0:02:33.240
Every day, we have to pay for the lodging place.

0:02:33.240,0:02:40.420
Now, they have asked us to pack out and we have no other place to stay.

0:02:40.420,0:02:42.060
How old are your children?

0:02:42.060,0:02:47.780
This one is thirteen years old and this one is five years old.

0:02:47.780,0:02:51.220
Please, man of God, help us!

0:02:51.220,0:02:54.380
Help my little family!

0:02:54.380,0:02:56.160
Where is your husband now?

0:02:56.160,0:02:57.960
I don't know where he is.

0:02:57.960,0:03:09.180
He went out in the morning as usual, hustling and he knows that we no longer have any place to stay.

0:03:09.180,0:03:15.620
I just decided that I cannot live like this any longer.

0:03:15.620,0:03:17.100
My name is Frederick.

0:03:17.100,0:03:21.680
I was born in Indonesia, then, we came to Nigeria.

0:03:21.680,0:03:24.980
Frederick Egesi.

0:03:24.980,0:03:30.460
Since that time, me and my mother and sister have always suffered, all the time.

0:03:30.460,0:03:38.600
Sometimes, we cannot eat and we didn't know what to do any longer.

0:03:38.600,0:03:43.640
In the village, they accused my father of killing somebody.

0:03:43.640,0:03:47.080
That was the problem that brought us to Lagos.

0:03:47.080,0:03:50.540
Food is very hard for us to get.

0:03:50.540,0:03:53.340
Before we eat…

0:03:53.340,0:03:59.660
In our hotel, we don't have money so, we are owing them.

0:03:59.660,0:04:01.080
They have sent us out.

0:04:01.080,0:04:04.600
They are telling us to pack out because we have not paid their money.

0:04:04.600,0:04:07.900
The money we owe them is a lot.

0:04:07.900,0:04:14.580
Since two months, we have been in Lagos and to eat is very hard.

0:04:14.580,0:04:17.260
My daddy – I don’t know where he is.

0:04:17.260,0:04:20.540
He went out in the morning and has not come back.

0:04:20.540,0:04:27.780
He used to go to Alaba and help people so they will give him money.

0:04:27.780,0:04:30.240
That is the only thing he used to do.

0:04:30.240,0:04:32.700
Sometimes, he will come back empty handed.

0:04:32.700,0:04:34.440
He would not hold any money.

0:04:34.440,0:04:35.560
Then, we will not eat.

0:04:35.560,0:04:39.840
We will just sleep until the next day.

0:04:39.840,0:04:41.640
He will be always owing people.

0:04:41.640,0:04:44.180
Now, we have a lot of debts to pay.

0:04:44.180,0:04:47.160
We owe a lot of people now.

0:04:47.160,0:04:51.160
This is our bag because they seized our other bag.

0:04:51.160,0:04:57.220
They seized it because we have not paid the hotel accommodation fee.

0:04:57.220,0:05:02.540
They seized it so this is the only bag we use to manage and come out.

