0:05:10.300,0:05:18.140
My sister's clothes, my mother's and my own clothes and a blanket.

0:05:18.140,0:05:21.500
These are the only things you have for you and your family?

0:05:21.500,0:05:25.300
Yes, the only things we have.

0:05:25.300,0:05:31.540
I came with my own passport but my two kids don't have any ID with them right now.

0:05:31.540,0:05:34.940
It is only me who has my own passport.

0:05:34.940,0:05:36.460
Can we see your documents?

0:05:36.460,0:05:39.120
Yes, of course.

