0:05:43.720,0:05:45.180
This is my passport.

0:05:45.180,0:05:47.740
It is only I who has a passport.

0:05:47.740,0:05:53.800
When we came to Nigeria, we used Travel Certificates.

0:05:53.800,0:05:59.420
Since then, they don’t have any ID, only I do.

0:05:59.420,0:06:07.900
We don’t have any money because since we came to Nigeria, nothing is working for us - nothing at all.

0:06:07.900,0:06:15.620
Please, we are coming here because we know there is solution in this very place – The SCOAN.

0:06:15.620,0:06:19.360
We used to see on Emmanuel TV that the man of God used to help people.

0:06:19.360,0:06:22.380
That is why this is our last bus stop.

0:06:22.380,0:06:26.920
I believe man of God, that our case will not run from you.

0:06:26.920,0:06:31.440
I believe you will help us.

0:06:31.440,0:06:36.940
I don’t even have one naira with me now, as I am talking.

0:06:36.940,0:06:45.360
Even my kids have not eaten since afternoon – we only had a little breakfast this morning.

0:06:45.360,0:06:48.660
Please, man of God, help us!

0:06:48.660,0:06:51.140
My name is Blessing.

0:06:51.140,0:06:55.000
My daddy is not around – he went to Alaba.

0:06:55.000,0:06:57.120
He is looking for money.

0:06:57.120,0:07:02.840
No food – we don’t have money.

0:07:02.840,0:07:12.180
The first thing the Emmanuel TV team did on hearing their pitiful plight was to take them in, give them a good

0:07:12.180,0:07:17.960
hot meal, something to drink, and the place to stay for the night.

0:07:17.960,0:07:21.620
Our first response as Christians is love.

0:07:21.620,0:07:29.500
No matter what situation we find ourselves in or what situation we are presented with; we should love first,

0:07:29.500,0:07:31.920
and walk in the light of love.

0:07:31.920,0:07:37.600
Love is the greatest because God is love.

